text: IOS 13 is a previous version of iOS, the operating system of the iPhone and iPod Touch. It was succeeded by IOS 14 on March 26, 2021. == Features == The iOS 13 has a features like dark mode options, new app called "Find My" which is switched by Find My iPhone and Find My Friends, changed contacts icon and many more. == References == ==Other websites== * 13 Category:Operating systems
title: IOS 13
